description:
Wada transfers from the Kansai region to the Toukai region in middle school. There, he meets and befriends Morino, Araki, Blanco and Ibata. The anime follows the antics and interactions of the five friends as they enjoy their everyday lives.
— written by Singan
Note: the characters` names are based on Chunichi Dragons baseball team which is located in the Toukai region.
